                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37037323/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2016-01-22 10:45
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="29089510">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/wildcat/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1775382-95.jpg" alt="無念" class="" /></a>
